# Session-local Claude Code state (worktrees, launch config) and ad-hoc
# root-level schema dumps - the schema source of truth is supabase/migrations/,
# with rls_grants_snapshot.txt covering the RLS/grants posture.
#
# The glob (rather than listing each dump) is deliberate: these accumulate one
# name at a time - schema.sql, then schema_review.sql - and each new one shows
# up as untracked noise until someone notices. Anchored to the repo root, so
# real schema files under supabase/ are unaffected.
.claude/
/schema*.sql
